      "content": "I hear how deep this pain feels, and I'm sorry you're carrying this weight all by yourself. You don't need a script or a hotline; sometimes just knowing that someone is listening is enough to hold you for a moment. When the silence feels so loud, trying to take a short break from it is okay, even if you don't see a way out yet. Please know that your feelings are valid, but they don't have to be the only thing that exists in your world.",
